y one of them, and the LORD is among them: wherefore then lift ye up yourselves above the congregation of the LORD?","year":-1471},{"id":"recXEKPvu66P3YSjq","ref":"Num.16.4","text":"And when Moses heard it, he fell upon his face:","year":-1471},{"id":"recTbVW6Xo5Xqe7mi","ref":"Num.16.5","text":"And he spake unto Korah and unto all his company, saying, Even to morrow the LORD will shew who are his, and who is holy; and will cause him to come near unto him: even him whom he hath chosen will he cause to come near unto him.","year":-1471},{"id":"recGqKBgXsi2VmzDY","ref":"Num.16.6","text":"This do; Take you censers, Korah, and all his company;","year":-1471},{"id":"recG4uAJcmMbdwdKt","ref":"Num.16.7","text":"And put fire therein, and put incense in them before the LORD to morrow: and it shall be that the man whom the LORD doth choose, he shall be holy: ye take too much upon you, ye sons of Levi.","year":-1471},{"id":"rec6WMTadva5R1gNa","ref":"Num.16.8","text":"And Moses said unto Korah, Hear, I pray you, ye sons of Levi:","year":-1471}]}
